80
00:07:12,000 --> 00:07:14,930
- What about the cause of death?
- Heart attack.

81
00:07:14,930 --> 00:07:17,870
I really don't believe things 
that aren't backed by science.

82
00:07:17,870 --> 00:07:20,770
